        "number": 7290,
        "title": "fix(buildURL): preserve encoded colon (%3A) for JSON-stringified params",
        "user": {
          "login": "Amaan-pathan",
          "id": 184144801,
          "node_id": "U_kgDOCvnToQ",
          "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/184144801?v=4",
          "gravatar_id": "",
          "url": "https://api.github.com/users/Amaan-pathan",
          "html_url": "https://github.com/Amaan-pathan",
          "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Amaan-pathan/followers",
          "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Amaan-pathan/following{/other_user}",
          "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Amaan-pathan/gists{/gist_id}",
          "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Amaan-pathan/starred{/owner}{/repo}",
          "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Amaan-pathan/subscriptions",
          "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Amaan-pathan/orgs",
          "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Amaan-pathan/repos",
          "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Amaan-pathan/events{/privacy}",
          "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Amaan-pathan/received_events",
          "type": "User",
          "user_view_type": "public",
          "site_admin": false
        },
        "labels": [],
        "state": "closed",
        "locked": false,
        "assignees": [],
        "milestone": null,
        "comments": 3,
        "created_at": "2025-12-04T13:43:20Z",
        "updated_at": "2026-04-27T14:30:04Z",
        "closed_at": "2026-04-27T14:30:04Z",
        "assignee": null,
        "author_association": "NONE",
        "issue_field_values": [],
        "type": null,
        "active_lock_reason": null,
        "draft": false,
        "pull_request": {
          "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/axios/axios/pulls/7290",
          "html_url": "https://github.com/axios/axios/pull/7290",
          "diff_url": "https://github.com/axios/axios/pull/7290.diff",
          "patch_url": "https://github.com/axios/axios/pull/7290.patch",
          "merged_at": null
        },
        "body": "**Description**\r\n\r\nThis PR fixes an issue where colons inside JSON-stringified params were not being consistently encoded. In some environments Axios was converting %3A back to :, while in others it preserved the encoding. This led to unpredictable behavior when APIs expected strictly encoded JSON in query parameters.\r\n\r\nTo address this, I added a small helper (isJSONLike) that detects when a param value looks like JSON (e.g., \"{...}\" or \"[...]\"). If the value is JSON-formatted, the colon remains encoded as %3A. For all non-JSON values, Axios continues to follow its existing encoding rules, so backward compatibility is preserved.\r\n\r\n**What’s Changed**\r\n\r\n- Added isJSONLike check inside encode()\r\n\r\n- Ensured JSON-stringified params keep %3A instead of decoding to :\r\n\r\n- Updated buildURL tests to cover:\r\n\r\n- JSON-like params\r\n\r\n- nested objects\r\n\r\n- arrays, dates, and special characters\r\n\r\n- custom serializer functions\r\n\r\n- URLs that already contain a query string",
        "reactions": {
