        "body": "**Description:**\n\nAfter logging into the E-Cell website, users are redirected to a dashboard. On this dashboard:\n\nThere's a section to submit your own project\n\nAnd a section to view other submitted projects\n\nEach project in the \"View Projects\" section has an \"Apply\" button. However, clicking on the \"Apply\" button currently does not trigger any action or redirection.\n\n\n**Steps to Reproduce:**\n\nLog in to the E-Cell website\n\nGo to the dashboard\n\nClick on \"Projects\"\n\nScroll down\n\nTry clicking the \"Apply\" button on any project\n\n**Expected Behavior:**\n\nClicking the \"Apply\" button should ideally:\n\nRedirect to an application form, OR\n\nOpen a modal to fill out application details, OR\n\nPerform the expected action defined for applying to a project\n\n**Actual Behavior:**\n\nNothing happens on click. No redirection, modal, or console error shown.\n\n_This screen recording is after login_ \n\nhttps://github.com/user-attachments/assets/d7449b33-ab84-4e2f-bf28-c28f49246855",
